以下是 Catfish & The Bottlemen 三年来的首场演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemens-first-show-in-third-years-setlist-watch-footage-3774311?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=catfish-the-bottlemens-三年内首秀演出曲目列表观看片段Alex RigottiFri, 12 Jul 2024 10:09:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3774311 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们迄今为止最大的头条节目是在即将到来的雷丁和利兹老虎机之前播出的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemens-first-show-in-three-years-setlist-watch-footage-3774311">《Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 三年来首场演出》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish 和 Bottlemen</a>三年来在利物浦塞夫顿公园举行了他们的首场演出 - 看看下面发生了什么。</p><ul><li data-listid="282"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2021-3031483"><b>2021 年雷丁节上的鲶鱼和装瓶工——一台可能会断电的光滑机器</b></a></li></ul><p>昨晚（7 月 11 日），这支威尔士乐队在 In The Park Festival 上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-announce-biggest-uk-headline-show-to-date-liverpools-sefton-park-3617964">表演了迄今为止规模最大的头条表演</a>，超过 32,000 名歌迷观看了乐队重返舞台。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mysterines">The Mysterines</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sundara-karma">Sundara Karma</a>也加入了乐队作为他们的支持。</p><p>这是他们自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-bondy-says-he-left-the-band-last-year-3240536">2022 年吉他手约翰尼·“邦迪”·邦德离开后的</a>首场演出，主唱范·麦肯和本吉·布莱克威成为最后剩下的成员。</p><p>这场盛大的音乐会也将在今年 8 月晚些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-six-headliners-revealed-as-first-wave-of-line-up-announced-tickets-3548085">在雷丁和利兹举行</a>，此外还有 7 月 19 日和 20 日在卡迪夫城堡举行的两场音乐会、8 月 24 日在爱丁堡的夏季音乐会以及 8 月 31 日在都柏林 RDS Simmonscourt 举行的音乐会 – 购买你的票<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcatfish-and-the-bottlemen-tickets%2Fartist%2F5121447" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>。</p><p>看看下面乐队的歌单，并观看粉丝拍摄的重要夜晚的片段：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们是鲶鱼和装瓶工<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" s