a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-share-comeback-single-showtime-and-announce-more-uk-headline-shows-3591486">Showtime</a> 》回归，该乐队此前曾在二月份在其社交媒体频道上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-post-clip-of-first-new-music-in-five-years-3589012">发布了一段 6 秒的曲目片段来调侃这首</a>歌曲。乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-announce-7-inch-and-merch-for-new-single-showtime-back-to-the-graft-again-3590146">发布了预购的 7 英寸白色黑胶唱片《Showtime》以及新商品</a>。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center">此外，他们的首张专辑《The Balcony》将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-announce-10th-anniversary-edition-of-the-balcony-3765408">发行 10 周年纪念版</a>，粉丝们可以期待 7 英寸的单曲盒装以及盒式磁带、黑胶唱片和 CD 版本。</div><div>该乐队还计划于今年晚些时候进行北美巡演。请参阅下面的所有日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-tickets/artist/2024302?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=WelXSo2cHxyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkCxAT3JV2coyY0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272">在此处</a>获取所有剩余门票： </p></div><div><figure id="attachment_3774372" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774372" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774372" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/catb-press-JOSHUA_HALLING-more-.jpg" alt="鲶鱼和瓶装工人（图片来源：Joshua Halling）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/catb-press-JOSHUA_HALLING-more-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/catb-press-JOSHUA_HALLING-more--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/catb-press-JOSHUA_HALLING-more--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/catb-press-JOSHUA_HALLING-more--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp