summer in conjunction with SM Entertainment.该剧将跟随五位英国选手通过韩国流行音乐培训系统，准备作为新的全球男孩乐队首次亮相。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kcon-la-2024-broadcast-live-primetime-cw-network-3774283">KCON LA 2024 to be broadcast live on network TV in the US</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
